     -1.19940   0.00000   0.00000    1
      1.19940   0.00000   0.00000    1
%endblock AtomicCoordinatesAndAtomicSpecies

XC.functional           GGA
XC.authors              PBE

MeshCutoff              500. Ry

SolutionMethod          diagon

ElectronicTemperature   1 meV
DM.Tolerance            1.0E-6
MaxSCFIterations        1000
DM.MixingWeight         0.005
DM.MixSCF1  F
MixHamiltonian  T
DM.NumberPulay          6
DM.NumberKick           25
